race.comment: HASIME (11) made progress last start when she did her best work late to finish second over 1600m at Warren. Well placed and there is no reason she cannot find winning ways. CHEEKY NUGGET (7) finished a length back from the winner last start at Bong Bong and is down in weight this time. Well placed here and should be in the finish. JOSHUA (6) was out of the money two runs back then again missed the frame last start over 1600m at Dubbo, beaten 4 lengths into fifth. Finds a nice race and can feature in the finish. TROPICANA'S CUBE (4) was well in commission last time out but could only manage to finish sixth over 1600m at Warren in a disappointing performance. Has his share of ability. Hard to beat in this suitable race.
